description: We offer Self-Guided Tours by Appointment Only. Surrounded by beautiful canyon views and easy access to nature trails, Montanosa apartments are your retreat in the coveted Tierrasanta neighborhood of San Diego, CA. Each of our pet-friendly 1- or 2-bedroom apartment homes features comforts like central air conditioning, an in-home washer and dryer, and a private, detached garage. Spacious floor plans with soaring ceilings and a fully equipped kitchen are found in every residence, while select residences boast extras like stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, and a cozy fireplace. Live each day to the fullest with easy access to our community amenities including three swimming pools and spas, two fitness centers, and our welcoming clubhouse. Enjoy additional perks like access to complimentary WiFi in many common areas, designated pet areas, and our resident lounge and game room. Living at Montanosa means having easy access to hiking trails adjacent to the property, as well as neighboring Mission Trails Regional Park. A short drive away, the beaches of the Pacific Ocean and nightlife of downtown San Diego and the Gaslamp Quarter offer you myriad of recreation opportunities. Our prime location in the heart of Tierrasantawidely considered one of San Diego's most desirable residential areasmeans your apartment home boasts close proximity to downtown attractions while offering a gorgeous natural environment surrounded by trails and parks.
